item.title: The more strange, the more users adopted a short-legged little black dog, half a year later, it actually turned into a long-legged big-nosed dog!
item.author: youremail@domain.com (Some Person)
item.description: The more strange the breeding, the more the netizens adopted a short-legged little black dog, half a year later, it turned into a long-legged big-nosed dog! Last June The netizen Ms. Huang adopted a small earth dog from the Internet. and named it Brown Sugar. Brown sugar is only 20 centimeters long when it first arrives at home. The little ones are especially cute. But I didn’t expect to keep it for only half a year or so.
